<h1><img src="../../../images/icons8/course-50.png"> Getting Started Guide</h1>

<p>
  The Hypercore Protocol is inspired by BitTorrent.
  It creates networked datasets which users can seed in a distributed mesh.
  It also includes a variety of tools for connecting devices, streaming data, and running services.
</p>

<p>
  To get started, choose how you want to use Hypercore:
</p>

